walker.easydb.datatype
Class EBinFile

java.lang.Object
  java.io.File
      walker.easydb.datatype.EBinFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.io.File>, UpdateIdentifier
public class EBinFile
extends java.io.File
implements UpdateIdentifier

二进制文件类型，它映射数据库的二进制大字段类型, 比如Oracle中的BLOB, 当向BLOB字段写入时,会用到此类型。 This class extends the File class, it reflects the binary type column in database, such as BLOB type of oracle. If you want to write text file into database, such as CLOB type of oracle you can using walker.easydb.datatype.TextFile.

Author:
Huqingmiao
See Also:
ETxtFile, Serialized Form
